tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE VoterTurnoutReports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age_group VARCHAR,
    gender VARCHAR,
    location VARCHAR,
    voter_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE voter_demographics (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR,
  location VARCHAR);

CREATE TABLE voter_turnout (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  voter_id INT,
  turnout_count INT,
  date DATE);
